ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
Kenichi Komaya has been named executive vice president of finance for Kawasaki 
Motors Corp. U.S.A. in Irvine. 
He was previously vice president of the department, and he also serves as 
treasurer and controller. Komaya joined the company in 1988 after working in 
the finance department of Kawasaki Heavy Industries. Bob Shepard moved from 
vice president to senior vice president, administration and information 
systems. Shepard, who joined Kawasaki in 1977, previously worked for Western 
Airlines and Boeing Corp. 
